        <item>
            <title>DJI 取消美國地理圍欄功能，將控制權交還用家</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/dji-will-no-longer-stop-drones-from-flying/life-tech/drone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dji-will-no-longer-stop-drones-from-flying</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/dji-will-no-longer-stop-drones-from-flying/life-tech/drone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 15:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[航拍]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[dji]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[無人機]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287309</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>DJI 無人機一向有地理圍欄功能，阻止用家將無人機飛進禁飛區域，不過他們最近公佈在美國取消相關功能，只會顯示可以關閉的警告來代替。<br /><span id="more-1287309"></span></p><p>DJI 全球政策主管 Adam Welsh 表示，由於美國已實施遙距識別（Remote ID）等監管措施，讓執法部門擁有執行現有規則的工具，因此公司決定「將控制權還給無人機操作者」，不再強行阻礙用家飛行。</p><p>不過近來美國對無人機安全憂慮增加，之前加州大火更出現無人機幹擾救援的事件，加上即將舉辦總統就職典禮，有意見認為 DJI 新政策的推出時機值得商榷。DJI 方面在官方網誌中就強調，此決定與政治無關，稱原計劃數月前就要推出此更新。而 FAA 發言人 Ian Gregor 則表示，聯邦航空管理局確實不要求無人機製造商實施地理圍欄功能，但此項自願性的安全措施移除是否會影響航空安全，仍有待觀察。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://viewpoints.dji.com/blog/djis-geo-system-is-an-education-not-enforcement-tool">DJI</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/dji-will-no-longer-stop-drones-from-flying/life-tech/drone/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>任天堂 Switch 2 正式亮相，官方影片揭露新機設計與功能</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/nitendo-switch-2-news/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nitendo-switch-2-news</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/nitendo-switch-2-news/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 14:04:24 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[nitendo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Switch]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Switch 2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[任天堂]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287427</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>眾所期待的任天堂 Switch 2 終於揭開神秘面紗。任天堂官方於今晚無預警釋出相關影片，新機外觀及多項新功能正式公開。</p><p>自 2017 年推出 Nintendo Switch 以來，這款遊戲機已進入第 8 年，不少玩家早已期待其後繼機型的到來。任天堂曾表示，會在本財年內公開 Switch 2 消息，而在多次傳聞與爆料後，1 月 16 日晚間 9 點，官方終於於 YouTube 平台公開長達 2 分鐘的影片，讓全球粉絲搶先目睹 Switch 2 的外貌與設計。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ffdgfdsgf-694x371.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="371" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ffdgfdsgf-694x371.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/ffdgfdsgf-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Switch 2 的外觀延續一代設計風格，但加入了多項改進細節。機身四周的接口重新調整，並新增更方便的 Type-C 插孔於主機上方，背面採用全新直立架設計，提供多角度擺放功能。控制器部分，搖桿與按鈕均增大以提升操作舒適度，背部更增設按鈕，可作為滑鼠功能使用。此外，Switch 2 預計於 2025 年內正式推出，並將於 4 月 2 日舉辦 Nintendo Direct 發表會進一步揭露更多細節。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287433" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1233-694x330.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="330" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1233-694x330.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/1233.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>任天堂同時強調，Switch 2 將支援向下相容，玩家可繼續遊玩目前的 Nintendo Switch 遊戲軟體，並選擇體驗現有遊戲中的下一款作品。Nintendo Switch Online 服務亦會延續支援至新機型上，為玩家提供更完善的遊戲體驗。</p><p><iframe title="YouTube video player" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/S1CbhpKC6SE?si=egpMrJM8JU4lnyCr" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><p>來源: <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S1CbhpKC6SE">nintendo</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/nitendo-switch-2-news/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Blue Origin 新型火箭首飛成功，將成 SpaceX Falcon Heavy 競爭對手</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/jeff-bezos-blue-origin-launches-massive-new-glenn-rocket/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=jeff-bezos-blue-origin-launches-massive-new-glenn-rocket</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/jeff-bezos-blue-origin-launches-massive-new-glenn-rocket/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 13:00:05 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[BLUE ORIGIN]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287296</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Jeff Bezos 旗下的 Blue Origin 全新研發的 New Glenn 火箭最近終於成功首飛，這款高達 320 呎的運載火箭預計將會與 SpaceX 的 Falcon Heavy 直接競爭，也為客户帶來更多選擇。<br /><span id="more-1287296"></span></p><p>New Glenn 火箭搭載了 7 具可重複使用 BE-4 引擎的 NG-1 火箭點火升空，二級火箭與載荷，在美國東部時間凌晨 2 點 03 分成功進入軌道，達成首飛主要任務目標。不過今次首飛也並非完美，火箭一級助推器在執行回收任務時，突然失去通訊並停止傳送數據，最終 Blue Origin 證實助推器在降落過程中遺失。不過總裁 Dave Limp 在發射前已經表示，本次無人飛行任務的首要目標是進入軌道，其他目標皆為「額外收穫」。</p><p>New Glenn 火箭歷經近十年的研發，運載能力與 SpaceX 的 Falcon Heavy 相當，未來將主要用於貨運任務。其中最受矚目的是為 Blue Origin 的 Project Kuiper 衞星網路計劃服務，預計發射 3,236 顆衞星，與 SpaceX 的 Starlink 競爭。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.space.com/space-exploration/launches-spacecraft/jeff-bezos-blue-origin-launches-massive-new-glenn-rocket-into-orbit-on-1st-flight-video">Space.com</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/jeff-bezos-blue-origin-launches-massive-new-glenn-rocket/fun-tech/">Blue Origin 新型火箭首飛成功，將成 SpaceX Falcon Heavy 競爭對手</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/jeff-bezos-blue-origin-launches-massive-new-glenn-rocket/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【教學】iPhone 動態島顯示農曆 + 天氣，一個 app 令動態島顯示不同實用資訊</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/iphone-dynamic-island-weather/tips-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-dynamic-island-weather</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/iphone-dynamic-island-weather/tips-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 12:00:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[實用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 16]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[動態島]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287164</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>最近小編身邊的朋友都紛紛升級至 iPhone 16，小編自己也從 iPhone 13 mini 升級至 iPhone 16，尚未太習慣動態島存在。今日小編想和大家分享一下如何活用動態島，讓你可以隨時檢視天氣、農曆日期等資訊。</p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="0116" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1047394327?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><h2>Step 1 安裝「鎖屏啟動」應用程式</h2><p>要改變動態島顯示資訊，無須 Jailbreak，你只需要安裝「鎖屏啟動」應用程式（<a href="https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E9%8E%96%E5%B1%8F%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95-%E8%90%AC%E8%83%BD%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E5%B0%8F%E7%B5%84%E4%BB%B6-%E9%9D%88%E5%8B%95%E5%B3%B6%E4%B8%80%E9%8D%B5%E5%BF%AB%E6%8D%B7%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%8D%B7%E5%BE%91%E4%BD%88%E5%B1%80/id1636719674">下載連結</a>）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287180" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1138-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1138-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1138.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲安裝「鎖屏啟動」程式</p><p>啟用應用程式後，會顯示下面畫面。記得要點擊右上角的「x」，<span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>不要選擇免費試用</strong></span>，否則 3 天後將會開始收費。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287186" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_1.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不要點擊「免費試用」</p><h2>Step 2 設定動態島</h2><p>之完成上述設定後會跳頁至下圖畫面，點擊右上角的星星圖案，然後選擇「開／關動態島」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287188" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_2.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲先點擊右上角「✨」（綠框示）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287187" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_3-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_3-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_3.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「開／關動態島」</p><p>接下來你需要開啟「靈活島＆即時活動」，預設為關閉。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287270" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_4-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_4-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_4.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲啟用「靈活島＆即時活動」</p><p>接下來向下滑動至「資料設定動態島」（紅框示），分別設定「左側顯示」與「右側顯示」選項，將選項改為「農曆（萬年曆）」以及「當前天氣」資訊。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_10-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_10-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_10.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲分別設定左右則顯示</p><p>先點擊「左側顯示」，進入設定頁面後向下滑動至看見「農曆（萬年曆）」並點擊之。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287275" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_9-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_9-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_9-1.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「左側顯示」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287273" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_8-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_8-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_8.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「農曆（萬年曆）」</p><p>之後點擊「右側顯示」，向下滑動至看見「當前天氣」再點擊該選項，最後按「完成」儲存設定。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287277" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_11-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_11-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_11.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「右側顯示」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287278" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unwire-1737012899-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unwire-1737012899-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unwire-1737012899.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇「當前天氣」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287279" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_13-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_13-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/launcher_13.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊完成方會儲存選項</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
