        <item>
            <title>澳網公開賽直播竟變 Wii Sports 風格，外媒：官方無轉播權出此下策</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/aus-tennis-use-wii-as-opening/life-tech/sport-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=aus-tennis-use-wii-as-opening</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/aus-tennis-use-wii-as-opening/life-tech/sport-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 11:00:58 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[運動科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[wii Sport]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[網球]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287254</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>澳洲網球公開賽今年出人意表，官方改用別開生面的直播方式，利用動作捕捉及 AI 技術，用卡通人物取代網球場上的選手。有球迷批評指，讓選手看起來就如《wii Sport》人物一樣。有球迷批評指這令球賽看起來非常兒戲。</p><p>據外國網球記者 Bastien Fachan 指，是次直播主辦方此舉並非單純創意，而是因無法取得完整轉播權，轉而選擇這一「權宜之計」。部分賽事由於官方無法取得傳播權，就採用動作捕捉技術配合 AI，利用卡通人物取締場上選手，令傳播看起來有如電子遊戲。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">The Australian Open don’t own all of their broadcasting rights (fairly common), so they’re live-streaming a Wii Tennis-like version of the matches on YouTube &#8211; love this 😂</p><p>This is Carlos Alcaraz’ match point: <a href="https://t.co/HvxhYneWGH">pic.twitter.com/HvxhYneWGH</a></p><p>— Bastien Fachan (@BastienFachan) <a href="https://twitter.com/BastienFachan/status/1878795279245476198?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 13, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><br /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287255" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/live_naomiosakavcaro-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/live_naomiosakavcaro-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/live_naomiosakavcaro.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@australianopen">Australian Open TV@YouTube</a></p><p>據《The Verge》引述澳洲網球公開賽創新總監 Machar Reid 表示，這項技術使用 12 個攝影機即時處理人體輪廓，並根據感應器收集到的數據以 2 分鐘延遲傳播現場賽事動畫版本。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287256" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/live_naomiosakavcaro-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/live_naomiosakavcaro-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/live_naomiosakavcaro-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@australianopen">Australian Open TV@YouTube</a></p><p>不過受現時技術限制，傳播偶爾會出現影畫不同步的情況，而且有時網球會離奇消失，同時細心觀察下會發現人物有時會沒有手指。不過對於想免費收看賽事的觀眾來講，算是聊勝於無。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287257" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/live_naomiosakavcaro-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/live_naomiosakavcaro-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/live_naomiosakavcaro-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@australianopen">Australian Open TV@YouTube</a></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_14447"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hr3R4FPwG_8?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E7%B6%B2%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%B3%BD%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E7%84%A1%E8%BD%89%E6%92%AD%E7%89%88%E6%AC%8A%EF%BC%9F%E6%94%B9%E7%94%A8-ai-%E8%AE%8A-wii-sport-%E9%A2%A8%E6%A0%BC%E9%87%8D%E7%8F%BE-120053512.html">Yahoo</a>、<a href="https://awfulannouncing.com/tennis/australian-open-streaming-tennis-wii-sports.html">Awfulannouncing</a> 、<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2025/1/15/24344285/australian-open-livestreaming-wii-sports-style-tennis-matches">The Verge</a>、<a href="https://kotaku.com/australian-open-wii-tennis-virtual-youtube-online-1851738723">kotaku</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
